1.Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Everybody knows that manual creation of graphics user interface tires
very much. In spite of introducing better kickstart (gadtools.library)
its took huge amount of time. Jan van den Baard made gui generator
'GadToolsBox', but he didn't implement source generator for E.
Wouter did an interim version of converter and Martin Kuchinka patched
its, but it wasn't good for me. I needed more useful tool. Thus
an idea of GUI for converter came into being. This converter is especially
for users without hard disks. Now you can save time wasted on unneccerey
loading of source generator.
This program is  GIFTWARE which  means that  if you like  the program  you
should reward the author with gift that, you think, matches his efforts.


2.Features
~~~~~~~~~~
    - full user interface
    - all GadTools gadget kinds supported (without a custom gadget)
    - GadTools menus supported
    - window flags and most tags
    - decrunch of powerpacked gui files


